title: Is It Too Late to Leave the Chat Group? - Novel Updates
tags: Fanfiction   Male Protagonist   System Administrator   Transmigration
author: Fleeing Cat   逃生的猫
description:
Ding! Welcome, He Who Knows Fate, to the Dimension Administrators Association!
 
Chen Heng had been feeling upset over the past few days, as he had suddenly gained an ability to see the future—the Absolute Future Sight.
 
I’m going to die! I’m going to die! These words were no exaggeration. Chen Hen would truly die in a few years.
 
Fortunately, there was a Dimension Administrators Association that could support and help him.
 
However, the moment he entered the association, a person called Magus of Flowers asked him to cross-dress and upload his photos. How do I deal with this nonsense?
 
So, is it too late to leave the chat group? Chen Heng felt that he had joined the wrong chat group.>
